F,|,ppApp,|,T,|,F,|,F,|,F,|,T,|,,|,,|,SoftMaker FreeOffice 2018,|,r931.0516,|,Office,|,SoftMaker FreeOffice, the free alternative to Microsoft Office.SoftMaker FreeOffice is a complete office suite with a word processor, a spreadsheet, and a presentation-graphics program:- FreeOffice TextMaker is more than just Word-compatible: It is not only great at document creation, but also at adding great-looking layouts.- The FreeOffice PlanMaker spreadsheet is not only Excel-compatible, but convinces with ease-of-use, speed, and presentation-quality charts.- And FreeOffice Presentations presents itself as a capable, easy to use alternative to Microsoft PowerPoint.[SoftMaker's FreeOffice can faithfully read MS Office documents, but has limited save-support. For example, TextMaker can faithfully read .doc and .docx files, but can only write to .doc format, not docx. For full docx (and xlsx, pptx, etc., formats) support you would have to acquire SoftMaker Office 2018 Standard or Pro.],|,http://www.freeoffice.com,|,5,|,%ppApps%\SoftMaker.FreeOffice.2018,|,%dbpath%/SoftMaker.FreeOffice.2018_r931.0516_ppApp.apz,|,%dbpath%/SoftMaker.FreeOffice.2018_r931.0516_ppApp.apz,|,%dbpath%/SoftMaker.FreeOffice.2018_r931.0516_ppApp.apz,|,%dbpath%/softmakerfreeoffice2018ppapp.png,|,38,|,%dbpath%/softmakerfreeoffice2018ppapp.jpg,|,%dbpath%/softmakerfreeoffice2018ppapp.png,|,,|,Word Processing|Office|Document,|,SoftMaker Software GmbH,|,,|,,|,,|,,|,2,|,r931.0516,|,2018-05,|,,|,,|,93404852,|,TextMaker,|,Word processor similar to MS Office Word,|,,|,Office,|,/home/glenn/.wine/drive_c/ppApps/SoftMaker.FreeOffice.2018,|,TextMaker.exe,|,,|,,|,,|,,|,,|,,|,,|,F,|,
